13686.name: Sealed Knight's Cloak
13686.description: Cloak with luxurious embroidery. When the seal is cancelled, it'll have Dark Attribute Defence +30 effect. The seal can be cancelled through the weaver Olf Kanore and Olf Adams. It cannot be worn before the seal cancellation. Enchantment, special abilities and augmentation are not possible. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

13687.name: Knight's Cloak
13687.description: Cloak with luxurious embroidery. Dark Attribute Defence +30. Can be worn by Barons or higher ranks of the clan that owns a castle. When an armor set above the Dynasty level is worn, the Sealed Cloak Slot will be open so that the cloak can be equipped. Enchantment, attribute, and smelting are impossible. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

13688.name: Knight's Cloak - Light Armor exclusive
13688.description: Cloak with luxurious embroidery. Dark Attribute Defence +30, and Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be worn by Barons or higher ranks of the clan that owns a castle. When the entire Vesper Noble or Dynasty set is worn, the Sealed Cloak Slot will be open and one can now wear the cloak. The cloak is exclusively for Bow Masters and Dagger Masters excluding Kamaels. Enchantment, special abilities and augmentation are not possible. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

13689.name: Knight's Cloak - Robe exclusive
13689.description: Cloak with luxurious embroidery. Dark Attribute Defence +30, and Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be worn by Barons or higher ranks of the clan that owns a castle. When the entire Vesper Noble or Dynasty set is worn, the Sealed Cloak Slot will be open and one can now wear the cloak. The cloak is exclusively for Healer, Enchanter, Summoner and Wizard excluding Kamaels. Enchantment, special abilities and augmentation are not possible. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

13690.name: Knight's Cloak - Kamael exclusive
13690.description: Cloak with luxurious embroidery. Dark Attribute Defence +30, and Cannot be exchanged or dropped. Can be worn by Barons or higher ranks of the clan that owns a castle. When the entire Vesper Noble or Dynasty set is worn, the Sealed Cloak Slot will be open and one can now wear the cloak. Kamael exclusive cloak. Enchantment, special abilities and augmentation are not possible. Cannot be exchanged or dropped.

13691.name: Mark of Keucereus - Stage 1
13691.description: Mark given to an adventurer who successfully completes Keucereus' order to break through to the Hall of Suffering. This mark is required for taking on higher level missions.

13692.name: Mark of Keucereus - Stage 2
13692.description: Mark given to an adventurer who successfully completes Kucereus' order to conquer the Hall of Erosion. Mark given to prove heroic achievements at the Seed of Infinity.

13693.name: Gracian Anniversary Coins
13693.description: Gracian Anniversary Coins. When possessed, a reward can be acquired. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, deleted nor stored in a private warehouse.

13694.name: Gracia Key
13694.description: You can acquire Gracia Anniversary Coins by using a Gracian treasure box. Re-use time is 10 minutes. Cannot be exchanged, dropped, destroyed, or stored in a private warehouse. Gracia Key
